message.body:
>>fbdc28e89d
Those are IPFS links, so you need IPFS: 
https://ipfs.io/

But you can also download the files without IPFS. Just replace the 46 digits hash within following link with the hash of the file you want to download, and then open the link in a web browser. Downloading may take a while, depending how fast the seeder is. 
https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmNZW6SUeWa8Lrjz7kLvAvxbF72FaDKnzFDUUNPHjp8ovP
